WEBVTT

761e7694-777b-48c0-b15b-e10e282de7e0-0
00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:02.920
When working on a document with
your team, you don't have to

761e7694-777b-48c0-b15b-e10e282de7e0-1
00:00:02.920 --> 00:00:05.400
call a meeting every time you
need to share notes or comments

761e7694-777b-48c0-b15b-e10e282de7e0-2
00:00:05.400 --> 00:00:06.040
with each other.

b044e125-5632-4fc9-95bb-dfbede3d3894-0
00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:09.038
With Microsoft Word, you and
your team members can add

b044e125-5632-4fc9-95bb-dfbede3d3894-1
00:00:09.038 --> 00:00:11.609
comments directly to the
document for everyone to see and

b044e125-5632-4fc9-95bb-dfbede3d3894-2
00:00:11.609 --> 00:00:11.919
review.

e31e4052-b47b-4603-afc9-83eea9fbc9e4-0
00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:15.569
This allows everyone to share
feedback and collaborate in one

e31e4052-b47b-4603-afc9-83eea9fbc9e4-1
00:00:15.569 --> 00:00:16.880
place, the document itself.

2c397510-010c-47ec-ae40-0c3b6faabb30-0
00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:19.790
To make a comment, lace your
cursor at the location in the

2c397510-010c-47ec-ae40-0c3b6faabb30-1
00:00:19.790 --> 00:00:21.440
document where you want the
comment to appear.

ce1c5264-c004-47df-9582-38d4d7100432-0
00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:24.484
For example, I'll lace my cursor
next to this logo at the top of

ce1c5264-c004-47df-9582-38d4d7100432-1
00:00:24.484 --> 00:00:24.840
the page.

c820285c-17de-4cb3-ab91-cd1f6209f644-0
00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:28.565
Then I'll go to the Review tab
of the ribbon and from here I'll

c820285c-17de-4cb3-ab91-cd1f6209f644-1
00:00:28.565 --> 00:00:29.400
click New Comment.

376f926a-cd08-4ab2-85c1-7316311c1210-0
00:00:30.330 --> 00:00:34.558
You can see it draws a line from
where my cursor was over here to

376f926a-cd08-4ab2-85c1-7316311c1210-1
00:00:34.558 --> 00:00:37.890
the side and I can Tye my
comment O it's that easy.

0e9b993b-57fe-4535-be7e-b27baa6ff062-0
00:00:38.530 --> 00:00:41.245
You can also highlight specific
words or phrases to alley your

0e9b993b-57fe-4535-be7e-b27baa6ff062-1
00:00:41.245 --> 00:00:43.530
comments to so it's clear what
you're commenting on.

a2bfa796-7e7f-4ae7-b757-af4c1f92fcc2-0
00:00:44.010 --> 00:00:46.506
For example, I notice that the
name of the hotel founder is

a2bfa796-7e7f-4ae7-b757-af4c1f92fcc2-1
00:00:46.506 --> 00:00:48.170
misselled a few times in this
document.

a392200f-576e-4276-8c04-b3f8b8f01bd0-0
00:00:48.930 --> 00:00:52.312
O I'll highlight one of those
missellings and this time I'll

a392200f-576e-4276-8c04-b3f8b8f01bd0-1
00:00:52.312 --> 00:00:55.806
rightclick on that and choose
New Comment and now I can Tye my

a392200f-576e-4276-8c04-b3f8b8f01bd0-2
00:00:55.806 --> 00:00:56.250
comment.

3e84de34-8118-4859-9b4a-fc6a64e57e27-0
00:00:56.250 --> 00:00:59.383
Just like before, you can also
read and respond to comments

3e84de34-8118-4859-9b4a-fc6a64e57e27-1
00:00:59.383 --> 00:01:01.420
left by others if I Scroll down
a bit.

a0d24258-e09a-48a1-a0a9-bd786915b1a6-0
00:01:01.620 --> 00:01:03.300
Notice here we have a comment
left by Jade.

f7404a3f-5a97-455b-b4cd-7ec52ab6f8d5-0
00:01:03.940 --> 00:01:06.665
When I roll over it, I can click
Reply to start a conversation

f7404a3f-5a97-455b-b4cd-7ec52ab6f8d5-1
00:01:06.665 --> 00:01:08.180
thread on this particular
comment.

9892ecd0-1eb0-42f8-a538-bdc4b20d675d-0
00:01:09.780 --> 00:01:12.510
You can also click Resolve when
an issue has been addressed that

9892ecd0-1eb0-42f8-a538-bdc4b20d675d-1
00:01:12.510 --> 00:01:15.240
Grays out the comments so others
can see that it's been handled,

9892ecd0-1eb0-42f8-a538-bdc4b20d675d-2
00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:17.634
but they can still read and
review the comment thread if

9892ecd0-1eb0-42f8-a538-bdc4b20d675d-3
00:01:17.634 --> 00:01:18.180
they need to.

919e76e5-9503-4957-aa3a-cdc3a2a19bd5-0
00:01:18.620 --> 00:01:21.157
If you want to remove a comment
entirely from the document, you

919e76e5-9503-4957-aa3a-cdc3a2a19bd5-1
00:01:21.157 --> 00:01:23.140
can use the Delete button here
in the Review tab.

a688cd7e-33b4-4bf0-9893-16f0787e77a8-0
00:01:23.940 --> 00:01:26.490
If you want to hide comments
from view without deleting them,

a688cd7e-33b4-4bf0-9893-16f0787e77a8-1
00:01:26.490 --> 00:01:28.260
toggle them with the Show
Comments button.

1fff679c-2494-4f90-b975-35cd42fd6e81-0
00:01:29.180 --> 00:01:32.656
You can see that hides all of my
comments and now I just see

1fff679c-2494-4f90-b975-35cd42fd6e81-1
00:01:32.656 --> 00:01:36.076
these little comment icons
indicating where they are in the

1fff679c-2494-4f90-b975-35cd42fd6e81-2
00:01:36.076 --> 00:01:39.667
document and I can click on them
to read them and if I want to

1fff679c-2494-4f90-b975-35cd42fd6e81-3
00:01:39.667 --> 00:01:42.460
see them again I can just click
Show Comments O.

24d4686c-a375-4bf6-afc2-0725ca6668a5-0
00:01:42.460 --> 00:01:45.459
As you can see, comments are a
useful tool for collaborating

24d4686c-a375-4bf6-afc2-0725ca6668a5-1
00:01:45.459 --> 00:01:47.820
and sharing feedback on a
document with others.